name: Volga-Dnepr Ilyushin Il-76TD-90VD [RA-76950] Landing and Close Up Taxi at Calgary Airport
description:
Seriously, 2017 has been an absolutely amazing year for special visitors in Calgary! Our latest rare aircraft is this Volga-Dnepr Ilyushin Il-76, the last visit of which was almost 3 years ago in 2014, with this exact aircraft. Here we have RA-76950 operating VDA5244 from Toronto making a very windy arrival on 35R and taxiing up close. ATC is included, hope you enjoy this fantastic Russian bird!

Thanks for watching!
